<div id='block_installer_linux_{{ revision }}' class="tabs__container tabs__container--descr active" markdown="1">

Log in on the **personal computer** to the container image registry:

```shell
echo <LICENSE_TOKEN> | docker login -u license-token --password-stdin registry.deckhouse.io
```

Run a container with the installer:

{% alert level="info" %}
If, with VPN enabled, the container with the installer cannot access the network, use the [instructions](/products/kubernetes-platform/documentation/v1/faq.html#what-to-do-if-with-vpn-enabled-the-container-with-the-installer).
{% endalert %}

```shell
docker run --pull=always -it -v "$PWD/config.yml:/config.yml" -v "$HOME/.ssh/:/tmp/.ssh/" registry.deckhouse.io/deckhouse/ee/install:stable bash -c "chmod 400 /tmp/.ssh/id_ed25519; bash"
```
</div>
